OL,3,CSurvivors of UVF gun attack settle
OL,4,Ccivil case in 'great victory'
OL,6,FThe PSNI and Ministry of Defence have
OL,7,Fsettled a civil case brought by eight
OL,8,Fvictims of a loyalist gun attack in
OL,9,F1992.
OL,11,FWhile the details of the settlement
OL,12,Fhave not been made public, it is
OL,13,Funderstood to involve compensation of
OL,14,Fseveral million pounds.
OL,16,FA lawyer representing the victims said
OL,17,Fthey had suffered "severe trauma" due
OL,18,Fto the shooting.
OL,26,@yD@SOUyD@aO]
