OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783675170
OL,3,CSurvivors of UVF gun attack settle
OL,4,Ccivil case in 'great victory'
OL,6,FThe attack was at the Thierafurth Inn
OL,7,Fin Kilcoo.JOne man was murdered and
OL,8,Fthree others were seriously wounded.
OL,10,FPeter McCormack, 42, was killed after
OL,11,Fa UVF gang carried out the shootings
OL,12,Fduring a darts tournament at the pub
OL,13,Fin November 1992.
OL,15,FA court had previously ruled that the
OL,16,Fstate has failed to carry out an
OL,17,Feffective human rights compliant
OL,18,Finvestigation into the attack.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
