FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783675170
OL,3,CSurvivors of UVF gun attack settle
OL,4,Ccivil case in 'great victory'
OL,6,FThe civil case was launched on behalf
OL,7,Fof a number of the survivors, who
OL,8,Fsuffered physical and mental injuries,
OL,9,Fand who alleged state collusion in the
OL,10,Fshooting.
OL,12,FAt Belfast High Court on Wednesday,
OL,13,Fbarrister Patrick Lyttle KC said the
OL,14,Fclaims had now been resolved in the
OL,15,Fcases of eight plaintiffs.
OL,17,FHe said one of the terms of settlement
OL,18,Fwas that the defendants would pay the
OL,19,Fplaintiff's legal costs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
