PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783675170
OL,3,CSurvivors of UVF gun attack settle
OL,4,Ccivil case in 'great victory'
OL,6,FThe barrister told the court he was
OL,7,Fannouncing the settlement on behalf of
OL,8,Fall of the parties.
OL,10,FSeveral survivors of the Thierafurth
OL,11,FInn gun attack were at the court,
OL,12,Fincluding Patrick Gribben, who was
OL,13,Fshot several times, and barman John
OL,14,FMcEvoy.
OL,16,FSolicitor for the victims, Gavin Booth
OL,17,Ffrom Phoenix Law said the settlement
OL,18,Fwas a "big deal for families in South
OL,19,FDown".
OL,26,@zD@GOU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
