PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783675170
OL,3,CSurvivors of UVF gun attack settle
OL,4,Ccivil case in 'great victory'
OL,6,FHe said: "It has taken 11 years since
OL,7,Fthe civil proceedings started for us
OL,8,Fto bring this to court but today is
OL,9,Ffinally an acknowledgement of the
OL,10,Fhurt, the pain and the trauma they
OL,11,Fcaused these families."
OL,13,FMr Booth added: "It is finally an
OL,14,Facknowledgement of what happened in
OL,15,F1992. What happened could have been
OL,16,Fstopped, those persons could have been
OL,17,Fprosecuted.
OL,19,F"The families have suffered severe
OL,20,Ftrauma.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@WO]uD@QOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783675170
OL,3,CSurvivors of UVF gun attack settle
OL,4,Ccivil case in 'great victory'
OL,6,F"Today is about the victims but I want
OL,7,Fto speak directly to the perpetrators.
OL,9,F"We know who you are, someday we hope
OL,10,Fthat you will be brought before the
OL,11,Fcourts and made answerable for what
OL,12,Fyou done."
OL,14,FMr McEvoy said the settlement was a
OL,15,F"great victory".
OL,17,FHe said: "We have waited a long time
OL,18,Ffor this, it is 34 years now from the
OL,19,Fshooting.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUtD@JO]wD@AOUwD@OO]yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
