OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,420,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783675170
OL,3,CSurvivors of UVF gun attack settle
OL,4,Ccivil case in 'great victory'
OL,6,F"It never goes out of your mind, it is
OL,7,Fwith you all the time."
OL,9,F"Compensation doesn't change what
OL,10,Fhappened, it doesn't change that those
OL,11,Fthat done this are still out there."
OL,13,FMr Gribben said he was glad the case
OL,14,Fwas over.
OL,16,FThe civil case took 11 years to reach
OL,17,Fits conclusion.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
